name: Rats Having Sex
description: This weekend, I enjoyed several events at Crypto Voxels, to take my mind off the problems with this rat and his girlfriend. When I got home, you don't know what I saw! They were having sex on the couch! They placed colored candles in the room, lit some incense and started the kamasutra. I'm too tired to deal with this. Leave them to the couch and let me smoke a joint in my room before bed.
